author: Lukas I. Alpert
title: Defining Moment for Dictionary.com: It’s For Sale
text:
Dictionary.com is for sale—you can look it up.
The online definition resource is being put on the block by Barry Diller’s IAC/InterActiveCorp, the company said.

IAC said it has hired investment bank Allen & Co. to explore a sale after two parties separately approached the company expressing interest in a possible acquisition of the property...
